# Using mongid for a rails project

1. Create defaulut rails project

2. Put following line to Gemfile
	gem 'mongoid', '4.0.2'

3. Install mongoid by run
		bundle install  # Install all missing dependencies
	or
		gem install mongid # Install only mongoid

4. Generate mongoid.yml
	gem g mongoid:config

5. Edit mongoid.yml

6. Change configuration follow mongoid installation document
	http://mongoid.org/en/mongoid/docs/installation.html